        Powerful Agent Tree
      </h2>
      <div class="h-1 w-16 bg-primary mb-6"></div>
      <p class="text-lg text-base-content/70 mb-6 leading-relaxed font-normal">
        Easily browse agent sessions and navigate directly to agents to make
        steering a breeze.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-base-content/70 mb-6 leading-relaxed font-normal">
        Agents are organized according to their team structure and highlighting
        indicate which agents are working so you can check on progress.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/birdhouse-labs/birdhouse/releases"
        target="_blank"
        class="btn btn-primary btn-lg mb-4 md:mb-0 gap-2"
      >
        <i data-lucide="bird"></i>
        Get Birdhouse
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="w-3/5 md:w-2/5 mx-auto glass p-2 md:p-12 rounded-lg">
      <div
        class="placeholder aspect-[3/4] rounded-xl shadow-2xl flex items-center justify-center"
