    <div class="lg:w-2/5">
      <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl mb-6">
        Save Winning Patterns
      </h2>
      <div class="h-1 w-16 bg-primary mb-6"></div>
      <p class="text-lg text-base-content/70 mb-6 leading-relaxed font-normal">
        Found a workflow that works? Save it as a pattern then reuse it with
        natural language.
      </p>

      <p class="text-lg text-base-content/70 mb-6 leading-relaxed font-normal">
        Patterns let you work faster by turning your favourite phrases into
        curated prompts. We've included several useful entries to get you
        started!
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="lg:w-3/5 w-full glass p-2 md:p-12 rounded-lg">
